      "source": [
        "# 🔐 SigAuth Backend v7 (Stability + Correctness Focus)\n",
        "\n",
        "This notebook is rebuilt to fix the **always-tampered** behavior and provide stable multi-class output:\n",
        "- **authentic**\n",
        "- **forged**\n",
        "- **tampered**\n",
        "\n",
        "## Key changes vs old notebook\n",
        "1. Stronger tamper training with **domain-robust clean negatives** (SVC genuine + forged treated as clean for tamper model).\n",
        "2. Separate threshold calibration for Siamese and Tamper model using validation curves.\n",
        "3. Final decision is calibrated multi-class fusion (not a single hard tamper gate).\n",
        "4. Exact-image hash short-circuit: if exact DB reference image is uploaded, returns authentic with high confidence.\n",
        "\n",
        "Upload exactly these ZIP files in Colab files panel before running:\n",
        "- `task1.zip`\n",
        "- `task2.zip`\n",
        "- `synthetic_tamper.zip`\n"
      ]
    },
